<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Women's Health Hub</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/womens-health.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Georgia&family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="lesson-nav">
        <a href="/dashboard/learn" class="back-btn">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7" />
            </svg>
            Return to lessons
        </a>
        <h1>Women's Health Center</h1>
    </nav>

    <div class="knowledge-container">
        <article class="research-paper">
            <h1>Comprehensive Women's Health</h1>

            <div class="article-content">
                <section class="intro-section">
                    <p class="lead-paragraph">
                        Empower your health journey with evidence-based guidance covering all life stages. From
                        reproductive health to menopause management, this resource provides essential information
                        for optimal physical and mental well-being.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="main-content">
                    <h2>Reproductive Health</h2>
                    <p>
                        Key aspects of gynecological care:
                    <ul class="womens-list">
                        <li>Menstrual cycle tracking</li>
                        <li>Contraception options</li>
                        <li>Fertility awareness</li>
                        <li>STI prevention</li>
                    </ul>
                    Regular pelvic exams and Pap smears are crucial for early detection of health issues.
                    </p>

                    <h2>Life Stage Considerations</h2>
                    <p>
                        Health priorities by phase:
                    <ul class="womens-list">
                        <li>Adolescence: Puberty education</li>
                        <li>20s-30s: Preconception care</li>
                        <li>40s-50s: Menopause preparation</li>
                        <li>60s+: Bone density management</li>
                    </ul>
                    </p>

                    <h2>Mental Wellness</h2>
                    <p>
                        Addressing gender-specific challenges:
                    <ul class="womens-list">
                        <li>Postpartum depression</li>
                        <li>PMDD management</li>
                        <li>Body image issues</li>
                        <li>Stress coping strategies</li>
                    </ul>
                    </p>

                    <h2>Preventive Screenings</h2>
                    <p>
                        Essential health checks:
                    <ul class="womens-list">
                        <li>Mammograms (40+)</li>
                        <li>HPV DNA testing</li>
                        <li>Bone density scans</li>
                        <li>Cardiovascular risk assessment</li>
                    </ul>
                    </p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </article>

        <section class="health-interaction">
            <h2>Women's Health Questions?</h2>
            <div class="query-container">
                <form action="/dashboard/learn/womens/generate" method="POST">
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <textarea name="question" rows="4"
                            placeholder="Ask women's health questions (e.g., 'Best exercises during pregnancy?')"
                            aria-label="Health question input"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">
                        Get Health Insights
                    </button>
                </form>

                <% if (responseText) { %>
                    <div class="response-card">
                        <div class="response-content">
                            <%= responseText %>
                                <p class="medical-note">Consult your healthcare provider for personal medical advice</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <% } %>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>

</html>